	<Property Name="NI.Lib.Description" Type="Str">This actor simulates a data acquisition process.  If its caller sends an Update message, this actor will send a single random number back to the caller.  If the caller sends a Start Acquisition message, this actor will send random numbers to the caller at a rate of 1 Hz, until the caller sends a Stop Acquisition message.</Property>
